### Remove a Came [DELETE]
+ Response 204

### Modify a Game [PATCH]
Modify a single game. Only can modify the top level fields using this endpoint.
To modify assistant referees use /tournaments/{tournamentid}/games/{gameid}/assistantreferees.

+ Parameters
    + tournamentid (required, string) ... The id of the requested tournament, case insensitive. 
    + gameid (required, string) ... The id of the requested game before the request. If id is included in the PATCH data it will 
change for future requests.

+ Request

        {
            "pitch": "5",
            "startTime": "2014-04-09T12:00+05:00",
            "headReferee": {
                "id": "40002"
            },
            "team1": {
                "id": "40018"
            }
        }

+ Response 200 (application/json)
    
        {
            "id": "90004",
            "pitch": "5",
            "startTime": "2014-04-09T12:00+05:00",
            "headReferee": {
                "id": "40002",
                "name": "Samy Mousa"
